<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pricing and Shipping Information - PingME</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      width: 90%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      margin-left: 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #222;
      color: #ccc;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #ccc;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Media Queries for responsiveness */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        width: 95%;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      p, ul {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }

      p, ul {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }

      footer {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Pricing and Shipping Information</h1>

    <h2>Pricing</h2>
    <p>Our prices for QR Code Decals vary based on size, design complexity, and quantity. You can find detailed pricing for each product on the respective product pages.</p>

    <h2>Payment Methods</h2>
    <p>We accept the following payment methods:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Credit Cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express)</li>
      <li>PayPal</li>
      <li>Bank Transfer (for bulk orders)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Shipping Charges</h2>
    <p>We offer both domestic and international shipping options. Shipping charges are calculated based on the destination and weight of your order.</p>

    <h2>Domestic Shipping</h2>
    <p>Domestic shipping within India typically takes 5 days to deliver.</p>

    <h2>International Shipping</h2>
    <p>We ship internationally to most countries. International shipping times vary depending on the destination and customs processing. Please contact us for specific shipping times to your country.</p>

    <h2>Shipping Restrictions</h2>
    <p>We currently ship to everywhere in India.</p>

    <h2>Estimated Delivery Time</h2>
    <p>Estimated delivery times:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Domestic: 5 Days</li>
      <li>International: 6-10 Days (may vary based on location)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about our pricing, payment methods, shipping charges, or delivery times, please contact us through our contact page.</p>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 PingME. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
